== 制作 ==
2014年9月6日，[[麥特·戴蒙|麥特·戴蒙]]宣布再次聯手電影製作人[[肯尼斯·洛勒根|肯尼斯·洛勒根]]製作《海邊的曼徹斯特》<ref name=DamonLonergan>{{cite news|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|last2=Siegel|first2=Tatiana|title=Toronto: Matt Damon and Kenneth Lonergan Reteaming for 'Manchester-by-the-Sea' (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/toronto-matt-damon-kenneth-lonergan-730704|accessdate=2015-03-25|publisher=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2014-09-06|archive-date=2015-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150408172719/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/toronto-matt-damon-kenneth-lonergan-730704|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此前兩人曾共同製作2011年電影《{{le|瑪格麗特 (電影)|Margaret (2011 film)|瑪格麗特}}》<ref name="DamonLonergan" />。影片原先打算由麥特·戴蒙執導，但由於檔期衝突，洛勒根取為執導，同時麥特·戴蒙保留製片人和主演角色。其後，洛勒根表示麥特·戴蒙和[[約翰·卡拉辛斯基|約翰·卡拉辛斯基]]已向他提出構思，卡拉辛斯基初步計劃參演<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/manchester-by-the-sea-the-story-behind-sundance-2016s-best-movie-20160201|title=How 'Manchester by the Sea' Became a Sundance 2016 Hit|last=Fear|first=David|date=2016-02-01|work=|newspaper=Rolling Stone|access-date=2016-11-12|via=|archive-date=2016-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161113055441/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/manchester-by-the-sea-the-story-behind-sundance-2016s-best-movie-20160201|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|琪琪·普利茲克|Gigi Pritzker}}透過名下公司{{le|零散娛樂|OddLot Entertainment}}投資影片<ref name="DamonLonergan" />。

2014年9月8日，前期制作启动<ref name="DamonLonergan" />。12月初，参演《[[怒海救援|怒海救援]]》的[[卡西·阿弗莱克|卡西·阿弗莱克]]向《{{le|波士顿环球报|The Boston Globe}}》透露他将代替麥特·戴蒙出演李·钱德勒一角<ref>{{cite news|title='Finest Hours' is the finest shoot for Casey Affleck|url=http://www.bostonglobe.com/lifestyle/names/2014/12/12/finest-hours-finest-shoot-for-casey-affleck/qYoKHiYcEZ0YaToc06U3UI/story.html|accessdate=2015-03-25|publisher=bostonglobe.com|date=2014-12-12|archive-date=2014-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141213064539/http://www.bostonglobe.com/lifestyle/names/2014/12/12/finest-hours-finest-shoot-for-casey-affleck/qYoKHiYcEZ0YaToc06U3UI/story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，这一消息于2015年1月5日正式宣布<ref>{{cite news|last1=Ge|first1=Linda|title=Casey Affleck Replacing Matt Damon in Kenneth Lonergan's 'Manchester-by-the-Sea'|url=http://www.thewrap.com/casey-affleck-replacing-matt-damon-in-kenneth-lonergans-manchester-by-the-sea/|accessdate=2015-03-25|publisher=thewrap.com|date=2015-01-05|archive-date=2015-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150324040119/http://www.thewrap.com/casey-affleck-replacing-matt-damon-in-kenneth-lonergans-manchester-by-the-sea/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。后来于1月9日，[[米歇尔·威廉姆斯|米歇尔·威廉姆斯]]加盟剧组，饰演钱德勒妻子<ref name=WilliamsCast>{{cite news|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|title=Michelle Williams Joining Casey Affleck in 'Manchester-by-the-Sea' (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/michelle-williams-joining-casey-affleck-762261|accessdate=2015-03-25|publisher=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2014-01-09|archive-date=2015-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150312163148/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/michelle-williams-joining-casey-affleck-762261|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年3月，報道指Sierra / Affinity將投資影片，{{le|金百利·斯圖瓦德|Kimberly Steward}}透過名下公司K Period Media資助影片。同樣投資影片的還有{{le|凱文·J·瓦爾什|Kevin J. Walsh (film producer)}}和{{le|克里斯·摩爾|Chris Moore (film producer)}}<ref name=Financier>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=Berlin: Casey Affleck's 'Manchester-By-The-Sea' Locks Financing|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/berlin-casey-afflecks-manchester-by-the-sea-locks-financing-1201418932/|accessdate=2015-03-25|publisher=variety.com|date=2015-01-29|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021000247/https://variety.com/2015/film/news/berlin-casey-afflecks-manchester-by-the-sea-locks-financing-1201418932/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片執行製片由喬什·戈弗雷（{{lang|en|Josh Godfrey}}）、約翰·卡拉辛斯基、克萊恩·鮑德溫（{{lang|en|Declan Baldwin}}）和比爾·米利奧爾（{{lang|en|Bill Migliore}}）擔任，普利茲克退出製作<ref name="Financier" />。2015年2月24日，[[凱爾·錢德勒|凱爾·錢德勒]]簽約劇組，飾演阿弗萊克的哥哥<ref name=ChandlerCast>{{cite news|last1=Rose|first1=Lacey|last2=Kit|first2=Borys|title=Kyle Chandler Joins Casey Affleck in 'Manchester-by-the-Sea' (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/kyle-chandler-joins-casey-affleck-777288|accessdate=2015-03-25|publisher=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2015-02-24|archive-date=2015-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150408121944/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/kyle-chandler-joins-casey-affleck-777288|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年4月，[[盧卡斯·赫奇斯|盧卡斯·赫奇斯]]加盟<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kilday|first1=Gregg|title=Lucas Hedges Joins Casey Affleck Starrer 'Manchester-by-the-Sea'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/lucas-hedges-joins-casey-affleck-787592|accessdate=2016-01-23|publisher=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2015-04-09|archive-date=2016-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160201094144/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/lucas-hedges-joins-casey-affleck-787592|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後加盟的還有{{le|艾麗卡·麥德蒙|Erica McDermott}}<ref>{{cite news |last=Jackson-Glidden |first=Brooke |url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/lifestyle/names/2015/06/