影片於2015年3月23日[[新英格蘭|新英格蘭]][[馬薩諸塞州|馬薩諸塞州]]同名城鎮{{le|海邊的曼徹斯特 (馬薩諸塞州)|Manchester-by-the-Sea, Massachusetts|海邊的-{}-曼徹斯特}}開拍<ref name="ChandlerCast" /><ref>{{cite news|last1=Rapalyea|first1=Taylor|title=Damon's 'Manchester-by-the-Sea' begins production in namesake town|url=http://www.gloucestertimes.com/news/local_news/damon-s-manchester-by-the-sea-begins-production-in-namesake/article_b99a812a-321c-56c3-9371-e8d2830ef6ae.html|accessdate=2015-03-25|publisher=gloucestertimes.com|date=2015-03-24|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002061921/http://www.gloucestertimes.com/news/local_news/damon-s-manchester-by-the-sea-begins-production-in-namesake/article_b99a812a-321c-56c3-9371-e8d2830ef6ae.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。次日，劇組移師{{le|北岸 (馬薩諸塞州)|North Shore (Massachusetts)|北岸}}<ref>{{cite news|last1=Luca|first1=Dustin|title=Freeze frame: Independent film 'Manchester-by-the-Sea' shooting in Beverly, North Shore|url=http://www.salemnews.com/news/local_news/freeze-frame-independent-film-manchester-by-the-sea-shooting-in/article_782873dd-0ee2-5353-8aad-5139b4fdd9d1.html|accessdate=2015-03-25|publisher=salemnews.com|date=2015-03-24|archive-date=2017-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107114523/http://www.salemnews.com/news/local_news/freeze-frame-independent-film-manchester-by-the-sea-shooting-in/article_782873dd-0ee2-5353-8aad-5139b4fdd9d1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

